.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2023-Elon-Musk-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，前 CNN 主播埃隆<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/elon-musk">·马斯克 (Elon Musk)</a>在采访中询问这位亿万富翁涉嫌使用氯胺酮的情况后，取消了与 X 的合同。马斯克此前<a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/zacharyfolk/2024/01/07/elon-musk-claims-not-even-trace-amounts-of-drugs-in-his-system-after-report-detailed-drug-concerns-from-tesla-spacex-execs/?sh=718de1f46348" target="_blank" rel="noopener">否认使用任何形式的非法药物</a>。</p><p>今年早些时候，Lemon 与马斯克的社交媒体平台 X（前身为 Twitter）签署了一项价值数百万美元的协议，以主办一个名为<em>“Don Lemon Show”</em>的新节目。</p><p>当时，莱蒙称赞 X 是“世界上最大的言论自由空间”。我现在比以往任何时候都更清楚，我们需要一个没有大厅监视器的情况下进行诚实辩论和讨论的场所。”</p><p>然而，<a href="https://twitter.com/karaswisher/status/1767948537784869361" target="_blank" rel="noopener">据科技记者 Kara Swisher 报道</a>，马斯克在上周五（3 月 8 日）接受采访后决定终止莱蒙的合同，“这并不符合马斯克的喜好，包括有关他使用氯胺酮的问题”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3511961" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3511961" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3511961" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Elon-Musk-main.jpg" alt="埃隆·马斯克" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Elon-Musk-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Elon-Musk-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Elon-Musk-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Elon-Musk-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Elon-Musk-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Elon-Musk-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3511961" class="wp-caption-text">埃隆·马斯克。图片来源：内森·霍华德/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>莱蒙在周三（3月13日）的一份<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4dfwV0RHX0/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">声明</a>中证实了这一消息，称他在接受采访几小时后就被告知马斯克将终止合同。</p><p> “他自愿同意接受采访，没有任何限制，我的问题是尊重的且范围广泛，”莱蒙补充道。 “我们聊得很愉快。显然他有不同的感觉。他致力于建立一个可以提出所有问题、可以分享所有想法的全球城镇广场，这似乎不包括像我这样的人向他提出的问题。”</p><p>莱蒙接着表示，他仍打算在周一（3月18日）发布对马斯克的采访，并将在 YouTube、X 和各种播客平台上播放。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4dfwV0RHX0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C55