a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fka-twigs">FKA Twigs</a> ）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tame-impala">Tame Impala</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kevin-parker">Kevin帕克</a>.</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-on-her-favourite-thing-about-glastonbury-3601162">Dua Lipa 发表的有关 Glastonbury 最喜欢（和最不喜欢）的事情的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
